snippet.title: Amber Heard petition under attack /Johnny Depp Real supporters
snippet.description:
A project was created by @johnnydepprealsupporters on IG. This aims to prove that JD's supporters are not paid "Russian bots". As part of the community who supports JD we're outraged that the signaturies have been accused of being fake accounts and all of this is a "smear campaign." 

Johnny was accused of orchastrating a paid petition to ruin AH's career and this made thousands of the signaturies irritated. Jeanne Larson who made the petition is a real person and so we are who signed it. Nobody forced us to sign. We aim to provide a voice to DV victims as abuse knows no gender.

Link to submit your support via DM:
https://instagram.com/johnnydepprealsupporters?igshid=atr7gisdyk3s

Link to the petition:
https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2

#Justiceforjohnnydepp
#WeAreNotbots
#Johnnydepp
